#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn74:10.1"
msgid "Tisso kho imā, aggivessana, vedanā—"
msgstr "There are these three feelings:"

msgctxt "mn74:10.2"
msgid "sukhā vedanā, dukkhā vedanā, adukkhamasukhā vedanā."
msgstr "pleasant, painful, and neutral."

msgctxt "mn74:10.3"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, aggivessana, samaye sukhaṃ vedanaṃ vedeti, neva tasmiṃ samaye "
"dukkhaṃ vedanaṃ vedeti, na adukkhamasukhaṃ vedanaṃ vedeti;"
msgstr ""
"At a time when you feel a pleasant feeling, you don’t feel a painful or "
"neutral feeling;"

msgctxt "mn74:10.4"
msgid "sukhaṃyeva tasmiṃ samaye vedanaṃ vedeti."
msgstr "you only feel a pleasant feeling."

msgctxt "mn74:10.5"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, aggivessana, samaye dukkhaṃ vedanaṃ vedeti, neva tasmiṃ samaye "
"sukhaṃ vedanaṃ vedeti, na adukkhamasukhaṃ vedanaṃ vedeti;"
msgstr ""
"At a time when you feel a painful feeling, you don’t feel a pleasant or "
"neutral feeling;"

msgctxt "mn74:10.6"
msgid "dukkhaṃyeva tasmiṃ samaye vedanaṃ vedeti."
msgstr "you only feel a painful feeling."

msgctxt "mn74:10.7"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, aggivessana, samaye adukkhamasukhaṃ vedanaṃ vedeti, neva tasmiṃ "
"samaye sukhaṃ vedanaṃ vedeti, na dukkhaṃ vedanaṃ vedeti;"
msgstr ""
"At a time when you feel a neutral feeling, you don’t feel a pleasant or "
"painful feeling;"

msgctxt "mn74:10.8"
msgid "adukkhamasukhaṃyeva tasmiṃ samaye vedanaṃ vedeti."
msgstr "you only feel a neutral feeling."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
msgctxt "mn74:11.1"
msgid ""
"Sukhāpi kho, aggivessana, vedanā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā "
"khayadhammā vayadhammā virāgadhammā nirodhadhammā;"
msgstr ""
"Pleasant, painful, and neutral feelings are impermanent, conditioned, "
"dependently originated, liable to end, vanish, fade away, and cease."

msgctxt "mn74:11.2"
msgid ""
"dukkhāpi kho, aggivessana, vedanā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā "
"khayadhammā vayadhammā virāgadhammā nirodhadhammā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn74:11.3"
msgid ""
"adukkhamasukhāpi kho, aggivessana, vedanā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā "
"khayadhammā vayadhammā virāgadhammā nirodhadhammā."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
msgctxt "mn74:12.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ passaṃ, aggivessana, sutavā ariyasāvako sukhāyapi vedanāya nibbindati, "
"dukkhāyapi vedanāya nibbindati, adukkhamasukhāyapi vedanāya nibbindati;"
msgstr ""
"Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with pleasant, "
"painful, and neutral feelings."

msgctxt "mn74:12.2"
msgid ""
"nibbindaṃ virajjati, virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ, vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re "
"freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed."

msgctxt "mn74:12.3"
msgid ""
"‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been "
"completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any "
"state of existence.’"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya13"></a>
msgctxt "mn74:13.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ vimuttacitto kho, aggivessana, bhikkhu na kenaci saṃvadati, na kenaci "
"vivadati, yañca loke vuttaṃ tena voharati, aparāmasan”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant whose mind is freed like this doesn’t side with anyone or fight "
"with anyone. They speak the language of the world without misapprehending "
"it.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya14"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.501"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
#. VAR: bījayamāno → vījayamāno (bj) | vijiyamāno (s1) | vijīyamāno (s2, s3) | vījamāno (pts1)
msgctxt "mn74:14.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā sāriputto bhagavato piṭṭhito ṭhito hoti "
"bhagavantaṃ bījayamāno."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time Venerable Sāriputta was standing behind the Buddha fanning "
"him."

msgctxt "mn74:14.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato sāriputtassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then he thought:"

msgctxt "mn74:14.3"
msgid ""
"“tesaṃ tesaṃ kira no bhagavā dhammānaṃ abhiññā pahānamāha, tesaṃ tesaṃ kira "
"no sugato dhammānaṃ abhiññā paṭinissaggamāhā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“It seems the Buddha speaks of giving up and letting go all these things "
"through direct knowledge.”"

msgctxt "mn74:14.4"
msgid ""
"Iti hidaṃ āyasmato sāriputtassa paṭisañcikkhato anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ "
"vimucci."
msgstr ""
"Reflecting like this, Venerable Sāriputta’s mind was freed from the "
"defilements by not grasping."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya15"></a>
msgctxt "mn74:15.1"
msgid ""
"Dīghanakhassa pana paribbājakassa virajaṃ vītamalaṃ dhammacakkhuṃ udapādi:"
msgstr ""
"And the stainless, immaculate vision of the Dhamma arose in the wanderer "
"Dīghanakha:"

msgctxt "mn74:15.2"
msgid "“yaṃ kiñci samudayadhammaṃ sabbaṃ taṃ nirodhadhamman”ti."
msgstr "“Everything that has a beginning has an end.”"

msgctxt "mn74:15.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho dīghanakho paribbājako diṭṭhadhammo pattadhammo viditadhammo "
"pariyogāḷhadhammo tiṇṇavicikiccho vigatakathaṃkatho vesārajjappatto "
"aparappaccayo satthusāsane bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Dīghanakha saw, attained, understood, and fathomed the Dhamma. He went "
"beyond doubt, got rid of indecision, and became self-assured and independent "
"of others regarding the Teacher’s instructions. He said to the Buddha:"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya16"></a>
msgctxt "mn74:16.1"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama."
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent!"

msgctxt "mn74:16.2"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā "
"vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya:"
" ‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti; evameva kho bhotā gotamena "
"anekapariyāyena dhammo pakāsito."
msgstr ""
"As if he were righting the overturned, or revealing the hidden, or pointing "
"out the path to the lost, or lighting a lamp in the dark so people with good "
"eyes can see what’s there, Master Gotama has made the teaching clear in many "
"ways."

msgctxt "mn74:16.3"
msgid "Esāhaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṃghañca."
msgstr ""
"I go for refuge to Master Gotama, to the teaching, and to the mendicant "
"Saṅgha."

msgctxt "mn74:16.4"
msgid ""
"Upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn74:16.5"
msgid "Dīghanakhasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
